  <description><![CDATA[<p>This well established hotel combines Alpine tradition with modern and friendly hospitality. Well known for its high-class cuisine, the restaurant is a highlight of the hotel along with the exclusive Feng Shui spa that follows the traditions of this relaxing and therapeutic philosophy. The Posta Zirm is a historical hotel in the centre of Corvara and a landmark known to generations of travellers. Nowadays, it has been transformed into a beautiful, high quality offering a warm welcome, excellent cuisine and fantastic leisure facilites. The Col Alto lift that links you to the Sella Ronda is just a short walk away.</p>]]></description>
